Barroso to Offer Tighter EU Cooperation Plan, Sueddeutsche Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-09-30T01:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/barroso-to-offer-tighter-eu-cooperation-plan-sueddeutsche-says.html
European Commission President  Jose Barroso  will make proposals in coming weeks on how to tighten
economic cooperation between the 27  European Union members  in
order to safeguard the euro currency and the union,  Sueddeutsche
Zeitung  reported today, citing an interview with Barroso.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
